  "description": "Practical Clean Architecture backend example built with FastAPI. No stateful globals (DI), low coupling (DIP), tactical DDD, CQRS, proper UoW usage. REST API, per-route error handling, session-based auth, contextual RBAC. Bundled with extensive docs and modern tooling",
